com.dropbox.core.v2.teamlog

Class FedExtraDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dropbox.core.v2.teamlog.FedExtraDetails

  • public final class FedExtraDetails
extends java.lang.Object
    More details about the organization or team.

    This class is an open tagged union. Tagged unions instances are always associated to a specific tag. This means only one of the isAbc() methods will return true. You can use tag() to determine the tag associated with this instance.

    Open unions may be extended in the future with additional tags. If a new tag is introduced that this SDK does not recognized, the OTHER value will be used.

        public FedExtraDetails.Tag tag()
        Returns the tag for this instance.

        This class is a tagged union. Tagged unions instances are always associated to a specific tag. This means only one of the isXyz() methods will return true. Callers are recommended to use the tag value in a switch statement to properly handle the different values for this FedExtraDetails.

        If a tag returned by the server is unrecognized by this SDK, the FedExtraDetails.Tag.OTHER value will be used.

        Returns:
        the tag for this instance.
